That's months away.

00:01:36.429 --> 00:01:37.555 position:50% align:center
[KANEISHI]
For real.

00:01:37.639 --> 00:01:39.182 position:50% align:center
[RANKA]
What about a haunted house?

00:01:39.265 --> 00:01:41.351 position:50% align:center
[KANEISHI] No can do,
I heard they were banned.

00:01:41.434 --> 00:01:42.602 position:50% align:center
[RANKA]
Why?

00:01:42.686 --> 00:01:44.312 position:50% align:center
[NAZUMI]
Ghosts might show up.

00:01:44.396 --> 00:01:45.522 position:50% align:center
--[YOMOGI] No way.
--[RANKA] What?

00:01:45.605 --> 00:01:46.981 position:50% align:center
[AWAKI]
Sure, whatever.

00:01:47.065 --> 00:01:48.775 position:50% align:center
[NAZUMI]
I'm serious!

00:01:48.858 --> 00:01:51.528 position:50% align:center
Supposedly, a bullied
student offed themselves.

00:01:51.611 --> 00:01:54.239 position:50% align:center
[RANKA] What if we cooked food?
What kind should we make?

00:01:54.322 --> 00:01:55.865 position:50% align:center
--[YOMOGI] Skewers?
--[RANKA] Fried food?

00:01:55.949 --> 00:01:57.701 position:50% align:center
--[KANEISHI] In class?
--[YOMOGI] Why not?

00:01:57.784 --> 00:02:00.120 position:50% align:center
[ALL laugh]

00:02:01.663 --> 00:02:06.668 position:50% align:center
